{"word":"ἐπακολουθέω","slug":"ἐπακολουθέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐπακολουθέω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ήσω</el>) </el><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to follow close upon, follow after</i>, <el>τινί</el> <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>;—<a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to pursue</i> as an enemy, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><i>to follow mentally</i>, <el>τῷ λόγῳ</el> <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>4. </b><i>to follow</i>, <a href='S:id est'>i. e.</a> <i>comply with</i>, <el>τοῖς πάθεσι</el> <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}